name: v1.5-beta, Upgrade ss-local and kcptun, support AEAD
body:
## Change List:

- Fix #283 
- Upgrade ss-local to version 3.0.5
- Update kcptun to version 20170322
- Support custom arguments for kcptun
- Represent proxy mode by status bar icon.
- Auto launch at login should be fixed.
- Better ss url parser.

## Changes List

- All in one preferences window.
- Configurable shortcuts.
- Deprecate OTA
- Better QRCode window

## Known Bugs
- #283

Fix bugs
